{"tid":2345782,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"BNO改名證明問題求救","createTime":"2020-12-29T19:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T03:04:24.000Z","uid":70037,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"89c7e1a3f38ef282a6d7fc417fc98c80e32f4efb","tid":2345782,"uid":70037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T19:56:15.000Z","msg":"話說我18歲換身分證嘅時候，加左nickname，當時入境事務處無比任何文件我，淨係張新身份證加左個名<br />\n<br />\n我寄BNO文件嘅時候，入面有埋去民政事務處宣誓既document. HM passport office最近叫我send多次文件去證明到我而家個名<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHM passport office個邊又accept statutory declaration or affidavit，咁係咪其實都accept民政事務署既宣誓？<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲遇到同樣問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eHUiExX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeHUiExX.png&h=fdb9dfbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1pRAGMi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1pRAGMi.png&h=ff972425&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"af2a17db439853266fab772c38deefdee7234e7c","tid":2345782,"uid":56624,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T20:09:14.000Z","msg":"佢個 宣誓 要按英國法律做，民政事務署嘅唔算。你可以搵律師做改名契，搵個有英國牌嘅律師宣誓，或者申請身分證登記事項證明書（三個做法都要俾錢）"},{"pid":"efbccc24343d51b1638f4cd0f82c7b13110177bc","tid":2345782,"uid":33059,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T20:14:26.000Z","msg":"加nickname型d?"},{"pid":"e7239916dcb4f9b40fafc25c45b23481df22ad77","tid":2345782,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T21:49:43.000Z","msg":"去入境申is okay<br />\n我都加咗nickname"},{"pid":"22527e4df9f5855cd4fda2700954a41c06cc4ade","tid":2345782,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T22:10:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a0e2fa4e7a79161f51df481b925fe6d5a8f53c0a","tid":2345782,"uid":384674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af2a17db439853266fab772c38dee